#include <stdio.h>
#define max(a,b) (a>b)?(a):(b);
#define min(a,b) (a>b)?(b):(a);

	int casenum,x0,y0,x1,y1,x2,y2,x3,y3,temp;
	scanf("%d",&casenum);
	for(int i=0;i<casenum;i++){
		scanf("%d %d %d %d",&x0,&y0,&x1,&y1);
		scanf("%d %d %d %d",&x2,&y2,&x3,&y3);
		if(y2>=y1 || y3<=y0){
			printf("No Overlap\n");	
		}else{
			y2=max(y0,y2);
			x1=min(x1,x3);
			y1=min(y1,y3);
			printf("%d %d %d %d\n",x2,y2,x1,y1);
		}
		

	}
}
